,Recommended,246620,10750728,"Posted: 24 June, 2014",all,novocain,"Very enjoyable game!Similar to the Flash game Pandemic(or Pandemic 2), if you have not played one of those and are interested in this game, I really do suggest totry them out first to get a feel for the type of gameplay.Plague Inc is essentially a more refined version ofPandemic, with more features, more gameplay elements, more intersting evolutions,more more more!Your task is simple; develop a pathogen to infect and kill the entire humankind. :)There are many different ways to achieve this goal and each time you manage to complete it you unlock a new type of pathogen and a new gene which can be used the next time you play.There are currently (24th June 2014) 9 different pathogens, for which you can select 5 gene slots, each slot has 5 different genes to choose from.Genes are a way to get different starting stats on your pathogen, for example ""Darwinist"" increases the chance of your plague mutating, ""Aerocyte"" increases chance of plague spreading by air. Your choice of pathogen and genes will affect your gameplay.The challenge of the game is to try and beat the game with all kinds of pathogens, they have different types of mutations that you can research with some unique attributes and abilities.The game is a tablet/mobile port, which is noticeable by some of the UI but in this type of game it isn't really an issue."
