,Recommended,246620,15288901,"Posted: 10 April, 2015",all,21Mars,Love the game
,Recommended,246620,9407815,"Posted: 10 March, 2014",all,BigBarazi,"This is a very creative genocidal game where you play as a plague, your mission: Destroy the worldyou start by creating your pathogen while choosing from different types: Bacteria, Virus, Fungus, Parasite, etc. each giving you special ""abilities"", like the virus being able to mutate fast or the Bacteria being very hardy and survivable in harsh environments. then you pick from several gene sequences that give you extra bonuses to certain attributes, like transmission by air or extra DNA (currency) to start withyou then pick a country to first infect one person there, from that person the infection starts spreading into other people in the country and into other countries. each country has certain attributes you need to look at. such as Canada being rich and cold, or China being urban or India being Hot,Humid and rural. these affect how your virus spreads and how you want to mutate it.you receive DNA when infecting people, that is your currency in the game, which you spend on gene modifications, those are split into Transmission which is how your plague transfers from one person to another, like by air, water, birds, rodents, insects, blood, and each corresponds to a certain country attribute, like insects thriving in hot countries and paying DNA into that makes it progress faster.Symptoms is the second plague feature, which can start with the cheap coughs, nausea, anemia and progress into Comas and Seizures and Heart Failure and Tumors which are completely lethal and what you eventually want to get to. be careful though, the more lethal the plague the more the world wants to cure it, but we will get to that laterthe last feature you can progress in is the abilities, like resistance to cold and heat which allows your plague to spread faster in such areas, or resistance to medicine in rich countries or hardening DNA so the cure becomes harder to make. in addition to this is the special abilities to the pathogen you have selected such as Bacteria hardening or Virus mutation speedThe failure state in this game is when the world discovers a cure and manages to wipe out your plague, this can be combated by being either very stealthy by not advancing symptoms while you infect the world as they cannot notice that they actually have the virus and then attack them in one swoop by spending all the DNA you accumulated over the years to get to the most lethal symptoms and wipe out humanity before it gets the chance. or by going super aggressive and killing people as they get infected, there are different possibilities and they all depends on what pathogen you pick really.another failure state which is very annoying is that some of the island nations (Greenland, Madagascar, Caribbean) can actually escape infection by noticing the plague and closing off borders, In my english video linked at the end of this review i have a situation where i wiped out the whole world and Greenland remained clean.to sum it up, this is a very fun game and is highly recommended. check my videos below for a video review in both arabic and english and don't forget to like and subscribe and share. also follow on twitter @bigbarazishowEnglish Video:http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mK4uC_TXbVghttp://store.steampowered.com/app/246620/#Arabic Video:http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NHCXCXeJGvY"
